You see the price is volatile.

00:55:57.440 --> 00:55:59.560
That's a doubling
in less than a year.

00:55:59.560 --> 00:56:01.570
That's a doubling.

00:56:01.570 --> 00:56:02.835
That's almost a tripling.

00:56:02.835 --> 00:56:03.835
That's another doubling.

00:56:07.330 --> 00:56:11.140
So historically, gas price
volatility not quite as

00:56:11.140 --> 00:56:16.610
bad as oil volatility,
but it's been there.

00:56:16.610 --> 00:56:18.560
We'll see going
forward the picture

00:56:18.560 --> 00:56:20.880
looks a little different.

00:56:20.880 --> 00:56:25.130
We'll see whether that's
likely to continue.

