RICHARD SCHMALENSEE:
Yeah, they built one.

01:04:05.480 --> 01:04:06.890
It may still be
working actually,

01:04:06.890 --> 01:04:08.840
but I thought that was
mostly for liquids.

01:04:08.840 --> 01:04:10.798
AUDIENCE: There's a
company here, [INAUDIBLE],,

01:04:10.798 --> 01:04:12.420
that actually [INAUDIBLE].

01:04:12.420 --> 01:04:14.683
That's pretty much just
the only place [INAUDIBLE]..

01:04:14.683 --> 01:04:16.850
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: That's
doing coal gasification,

01:04:16.850 --> 01:04:19.010
but that's not for use as gas.

01:04:19.010 --> 01:04:21.860
It's probably for use in
